task.summary: Adding Edge, DirectedEdge, and Vertex with tests.
Added EventBus. Moved Edge and Vertex as inner classes of Graph.
Adding events. Switched to using strings for ids.

Added with methods to EdgeAttributeEvent Refactored Event to include graph object IdentifiedElement - Fixed issues in putAll. If id is included it was ignored. This change will set id. - Added remove methods.
Fixed remove in Graph. Fixed remove and replaceAll in IdentifiedElement so id is always set.
Adding FromToElement so Edge does not need so many methods. Edge can focus on interactions with Graph.
Fixing putAll in FromToElement to handle 'from' and 'to' correctly Added setFrom and setTo implementation
Edge and Vertex constructors are now private.
Adding adjacentEdges to Vertex. Tests for Edge.from() and Edge.to().
